<p class="courseblockdesc">
Health promotion evaluation issues pertaining to people with disabilities will be critiqued and analyzed in relationship to application and usability. The content will build upon basic concepts discussed in <a href="/search/?P=DHD%20537" title="DHD&#160;537" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DHD 537');">DHD&#160;537</a>. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=DHD%20537" title="DHD&#160;537" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DHD 537');">DHD&#160;537</a>.<br />
