<p class="courseblockdesc">
Focuses on issues of wheelchair seating, positioning and mobility for children and adults with physical disabilities. Assessment procedures, technology selection, current research and analysis of funding sources. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=DHD%20440" title="DHD&#160;440" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DHD 440');">DHD&#160;440</a> or consent of the instructor. Recommended background: Physical therapy, occupational therapy, speech-language pathology, special education, engineering.<br />
