<p class="courseblockdesc">
Augmentative communication assessment strategies and evaluation of materials development. Utilizes case examples for discussion of specific approaches for different ages, disabilities, and settings. Course Information: Prerequisite(s):  <a href="/search/?P=DHD%20440" title="DHD&#160;440" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DHD 440');">DHD&#160;440</a>.  Recommended background:  Speech-Language Pathology, Occupational Therapy, Special Education.<br />
