<p class="courseblockdesc">
An introduction to the delivery of assistive technology (AT) services in the PreK-12 educational setting. Includes the legal foundation, models of AT service delivery, and practical components of AT consideration, assessment, and documentation. Course Information: Prerequisite(s): <a href="/search/?P=DHD%20440" title="DHD&#160;440" class="bubblelink code" onclick="return showCourse(this, 'DHD 440');">DHD&#160;440</a>.<br />
